BotGate v2.2 - TCP bot gate for
any telnet BBS. Callers must press
ESC/* twice before reaching your
real BBS. Custom ANSI prompts w/
live countdown. Synchronet-style
.can blocklists, IP2Location geo-
blocking, reverse-DNS matching,
auto rate-limit temp-bans. Pure
Python3, zero deps. Linux/Win/Mac.
Built for Spitfire, works anywhere.
